room_title: Escape room "Escape From Jose Gaspar's Pirate Ship" by Can You Escape? in Tampa
room_description: Two hundred years ago Jose Gaspar's ship, Floriblanca, sank beneath the stormy waves in a fiery battle at sea. The ship was believed to have been filled to the brim with gold, jewels, and other long-lost treasures, fruits of forty years of plundering the Florida seas. Climb aboard the legendary pirate ship as you hunt for the lost treasure and discover the truth behind the demise of Jose Gaspar.
